After a homely and unpopular teen accidentally dies because of a cruel prank played by her classmates, she comes back to life as a sexy seductress to exact revenge on her former tormenters. Jenna Dewan stars in this stylish shocker. Matthew Marsden, Chad Faust, Gil Hacohen. Directed by Jeremy Haft.
